      "rationale": "Three hexahedral-dominant meshes (2.1M, 5.8M, 14.7M cells) with r = 1.41. GCI on RH index: 2.1% (fine-to-medium), 2.8% (medium-to-coarse). Asymptotic range confirmed (GCI ratio 0.97). Achieved level 3 (GCI < 3%) exceeds required level 2."
