      "rationale": "All five operating points (3–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM) replicated using time-averaged inlet velocity profiles from FDA benchmark measurements. Blood viscosity set to Newtonian 0.0035 Pa·s consistent with experimental protocol. Inlet turbulence intensity matched to measured 4.2%. All BCs within ±3% of experimental values."
