    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors not assessed are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. RH < 1 confirmed across all five CPB operating points. GCI < 3% on primary QoI. Validation activities directly relevant to COU operating envelope. The hemolysis modeling methodology is consistent with current best practice as documented in the literature, including the approach benchmarked in the source referenced via referencesIdentifier. Credibility assessment supports regulatory submission for Class II CPB device.",
